h: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgroun=
d-color: #ccc;"> 558.7 million shares</a> outstanding, at $0.2961 each. Yes=
terday, April 23, when it <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/31266131.261440/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGV=
