; background-color: #ccc;">  discussed</a> in <a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/31266131.261440/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmN=
vbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDItMDgvYmVkLWJhdGgtYmV5b25kLWdvdC1pdHMtZG=
