<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31266131.261440/aH=
R0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMzAvYmVkL=
WJhdGgtYmV5b25kLWhhcy1tb3JlLXN0b2NrLXRvLXNlbGw_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQyNDIzX01PTkVZ=
U1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjM=
